	<h1>What is OpenPath?</h1>
	<p>OpenPath enables place-based learning. It uses location-based videochat sessions to connect learners to events at museums, libraries, parks, makerspaces, and more. Check out the latest on our dev blog found at <a href="http://openpathme.tumblr.com/" target="_blank">http://openpathme.tumblr.com/</a></p>
